  "identifier": "opencodebooks",
  "description": "Provides a minimal interface to define codebooks as data frames or CSV files and publish them as human-readable HTML and machine-readable SKOS/Turtle with stable hash URIs. Codebooks can be linked to datasets created with the 'dataset' package and harmonized with 'retroharmonize'. This is the reference implementation of the 'Open Codebooks' approach, designed to be easily replicated in other languages.",
